        <message>You can see your remaining sick leave days as follows:
1. On Workday, click on the cloud icon or your profile. From the dropdown, select **view profile** 
2. Underneath your name and surname on the left of your screen, select **Time off**
3. Select **Time off balance**
4. Click on **View Time Off balance**
5. All types of leave will appear. Your balance can be seen as **Sick Benefit Leave**.</message>
